soviet activist andrei d sakharov has been told 
that russian helicopter gunships fired on their own ground troops to 
prevent their capture by afgan rebels his soninlaw said tuesday 
night 
in the soviet union lt gen boris gromov who led the last 
contingent of soviet troops out of afghanistan on feb 14 said the 
allegation was monstrous 
