an example of the speech demons targeted for 
extinction in the new york city schools 
fred says he wasnt doin nuttin so i says to him im 
goin to da liberry ill meetcha there but he didnt know where 
da liberry was at i axe him are youse foolin round its like 
in midtown you know pacifically at da caunuh of 41st and fifth 
he axes me if i was ony goin to da liberry no i says whatcha 
doin next he axed first i says im goin to da museum to 
see some pitchers then im goin to see lorenzo he be sick and 
he aint got no food i brang some soup for him i says i think 
this is da right thing to do yup you betcha fred says 
now the same encounter rendered in proper english 
fred said he wasnt doing anything i told him im going to 
the library ill meet you there he didnt know where the library 
was i asked him are you fooling around its in midtown 
specifically its at the corner of 41st street and fifth avenue 
he asked me if i was going only to the library no i said what 
are you doing next he asked first i said im going to the 
museum to see some pictures then im going to see lorenzo hes 
sick and he has no food i brought some soup for him i said i 
thought this was the right thing to do yes youre right fred 
said 
