rupees 547 billion in the 198990 fiscal year which runs from 
april 1 through march 31 in 198889 the total budget was 7356 
billion rupees 566 billion 
in february 1988 the exchange rate was an estimated 12 rupees to 
1 the current rate is 15 rupees to 1 
