not to smoke in halls outside classrooms ms speer said smoking is 
also prohibited inside classrooms 
the nursing students lounge is divided for smokers and 
nonsmokers and staff members have separate lounges she said 
although the school is sensitive to the issues of tobacco 
farmers it also wants to provide a healthful environment to 
nonsmokers she said 
there are very few people in our area who smoke anymore she 
said its just like people have learned 
