raise or lower rates for various customers and said he would look at 
other safeguards to ensure price changes for less populated regions 
remain within the zone of reasonableness 
he said atampt would have to cut overall prices by 3 percent over 
four years under the fcc plan 
patrick also sought to mollify congress by proposing to divide 
atampts services into three baskets one group including 
residential and small business customers for example and allowing 
only limited price increases or decreases for each service 
