refrigerator 
sears switch to everyday low pricing a strategy pioneered by 
discount chains and adapted successfully last year by chicagobased 
montgomery ward amp co makes sears comparable to the discounters in 
price but not in looks 
although shoppers found some merchandise displayed in 
warehouselike stacks most of the goods were shown in the more 
